description: Fridas Cocina is an amazing gourmet Baja cuisine truck serving the San Diego area with delicious tacos, empanadas, burritos, and more. The truck began as a startup run by two single mothers, who wanted to create a living for themselves while bringing tasty seafood to the streets, and boy did they succeed. If you want to get a great meal while supporting two great ladies, nowhere is better than Fridas Cocina!
name: Fridas Cocina
